:'''Fidora's Robot:''' Hello, (Trailblazer). I am gathering datasets that can be used for emotional interactivity.
:'''Fidora's Robot:''' My master Fidora said that you can provide me with a suitable dataset. During the learning process, I will randomly present you with a social interaction. Please answer based on your personal experiences.
:'''Fidora's Robot:''' Your conversation will be recorded and parsed word-by-word.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'll have to choose carefully...
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Things are starting to get a little tense...
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_411160119-->
:'''Fidora's Robot:''' Initiating learning phase: Are you ready?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Ready.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_411160122-->
::'''Fidora's Robot:''' Scenario 1.
::'''Fidora's Robot:''' Fidora has been in high spirits lately, and she invites me to watch a bout at the Fight Club.
::'''Fidora's Robot:''' After the winning punch from the boxer Fidora is backing, she looks at me in anticipation of me saying something.
::'''Fidora's Robot:''' As her friend, what should my reply be at this time?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Training01_Loop-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Training01_Loop-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Describe the scenario for me once more.
